# Nemo URL Reference

Replace `<server-ip>` with the machine hosting Nemo.

Base:
- `http://<server-ip>:8000/`

Frontend Sections:
- Codex: `http://<server-ip>:8000/codex`
- Ishtar: `http://<server-ip>:8000/ishtar`
- Relay: `http://<server-ip>:8000/relay`
- Akashic proxy: `http://<server-ip>:8000/akashic`
- H-TV proxy: `http://<server-ip>:8000/htv`
- Voyager proxy: `http://<server-ip>:8000/voyager`

Section API Roots:
- Codex API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/codex`
- Ishtar API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/ishtar`
- Relay API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/relay`
- Gates API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates`
- Startup Services API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services`
- Priestess API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/priestess`
- DNS API: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/dns`

Gate Catalog:
- All Jellyfin gates status: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates`
- All Jellyfin gates metadata: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/meta/catalog`

Startup Services:
- All startup service status: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services`
- Startup service metadata: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/meta/catalog`

Tailscale:
- Check: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/tailscale/check`
- Start: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/tailscale/start`
- Stop managed process: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/tailscale/stop`

AdGuard:
- Check: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/adguard/check`
- Start: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/adguard/start`
- Stop managed process: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/startup-services/adguard/stop`
- Auto-start now defaults to off; Nemo's built-in DNS resolver replaces AdGuard for `chaldeas.home`.

Nemo DNS:
- Status: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/dns`
- `NEMO_DNS_ENABLED`: defaults to `true`.
- `NEMO_DNS_HOSTNAME`: defaults to `chaldeas.home`.
- `NEMO_DNS_RESOLVE_IP`: set this to Armando-GP's Tailscale IP, e.g. `100.111.90.10`.
- `NEMO_DNS_UPSTREAM`: defaults to `1.1.1.1`.
- `NEMO_DNS_PORT`: defaults to UDP `53`; Windows usually requires Administrator.

Startup Service Environment:
- `TAILSCALE_EXE`: defaults to `C:\Program Files\Tailscale\tailscale-ipn.exe`
- `TAILSCALE_COMMAND`: overrides the Tailscale command entirely.
- `NEMO_AUTOSTART_TAILSCALE`: defaults to `1`.
- `TAILSCALE_VISIBLE_CONSOLE`: defaults to `0`.
- `ADGUARD_EXE`: defaults to `C:\Program Files\AdGuardHome\AdGuardHome.exe`
- `ADGUARD_COMMAND`: overrides the AdGuard command entirely.
- `ADGUARD_CWD`: working directory for AdGuard.
- `NEMO_AUTOSTART_ADGUARD`: defaults to `1`.
- `ADGUARD_VISIBLE_CONSOLE`: defaults to `1`, so AdGuard opens with a terminal window.

Priestess Alerts:
- Status: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/priestess/status`
- Test Discord alert: `POST http://<server-ip>:8000/api/priestess/test`

Priestess Environment:
- `PRIESTESS_SERVICE_NAME`: display name, defaults to `Priestess`.
- `PRIESTESS_ENABLED`: defaults to `1`.
- `PRIESTESS_DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL`: Discord webhook URL for the alert channel.
- `PRIESTESS_DISCORD_USERNAME`: webhook username, defaults to the service name.
- `PRIESTESS_DISCORD_MENTION`: optional Discord mention for push alerts, e.g. `<@&ROLE_ID>`.
- `PRIESTESS_RELAY_ALERTS_ENABLED`: defaults to `1`.

Jellyfin Gates:

Akashic:
- Check: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/akashic/check`
- Start: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/akashic/start`
- Stop: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/akashic/stop`
- Open: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/akashic/open`
- Private Loader: `http://<server-ip>:8000/private/gates/akashic/loader`

H-TV:
- Check: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/htv/check`
- Start: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/htv/start`
- Stop: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/htv/stop`
- Open: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/htv/open`
- Private Loader: `http://<server-ip>:8000/private/gates/htv/loader`

Voyager:
- Check: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/voyager/check`
- Start: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/voyager/start`
- Stop: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/voyager/stop`
- Open: `http://<server-ip>:8000/api/gates/voyager/open`
- Private Loader: `http://<server-ip>:8000/private/gates/voyager/loader`

Notes:
- `start` spins up the Jellyfin gate under Nemo management.
- `stop` shuts it down.
- `check` returns current status.
- `open` now targets Nemo's private gate loader route after ensuring the gate is available.
- `private/gates/.../loader` serves the loader page directly and then redirects to the actual gate when ready.
- For path-based proxying, set Jellyfin Dashboard -> Settings -> Networking -> Base URL to `/akashic`, `/htv`, and `/voyager` respectively.
- For `chaldeas.home`, configure Tailscale Split DNS to point that hostname at Nemo's Tailscale IP and remove AdGuard as a global DNS override.
